498
00:25:09,291 --> 00:25:10,458
[KOBAYASHI]
No, not you.

499
00:25:10,541 --> 00:25:11,416
[TOHRU]
What else?

500
00:25:11,500 --> 00:25:12,625
[KOBAYASHI]
I dunno, peace.

501
00:25:12,708 --> 00:25:14,208
[TOHRU] So you're saying
I'm enough for you?

502
00:25:14,291 --> 00:25:15,791
